'''量子生物学'''是利用[[量子理论|量子理论]]来研究[[生命科学|生命科学]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Tae-Chang Kim| first = Eric Chaisson | title = Science, Education and Future Generations| publisher = Taylor & Francis Ltd| date = 1999| pages = 26| isbn = 978-9057005381}}</ref>的一门学科。该学科包含利用[[量子力学|量子力学]]研究[[生物过程|生物过程]]和[[分子动态结构|分子动态结构]]。利用量子生物学研究量子水平的分子动态结构和能量转移，如果所得结果与宏观的生物学现象相吻合且很难用其他学科的研究重复，则这一研究结果较为可信<ref>{{cite book | last = Ian Brown| first = Zengliang Yu, Thiraphat Vilaithong | title = Introduction to Ion Beam Biotechnology| publisher = Springer-Verlag New York Inc| date = 2005| pages = 97| isbn = 978-0387255316}}</ref>。

[[量子生物化学|量子生物化学]]和[[光合过程|光合过程]]的量子研究已得到了可核查的重要的结果。尤其是[[光合作用|光合作用]]中，对于俘获[[光子|光子]]后发生的分步的、对[[质子|质子]]的量子式释放，利用量子生物学的理论，已获得显著的研究进展（相关理论涉及到较为复杂的[[光系统II|光系统II]]）。此外，实验和理论的发现都支持[[酶促反应|酶促反应]]中包含[[量子隧穿效应|量子穿隧]]机制。将能量转化为化学能（可用于化学转化）的生物学过程在实质上都是[[量子力学过程|量子力学过程]]。这些过程包含[[化学反应|化学反应]]、[[光俘获|光俘获]]、[[电子|电子]][[激发态|激发态]]的形成、[[激发能|激发能]]的转移和[[化学过程|化学过程]]（如光合作用及[[细胞呼吸|细胞呼吸]]）中电子及质子（[[氢|氢]][[离子|离子]]）的转移<ref>Quantum Biology. University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign, Theoretical and Computational Biophysics Group. http://www.ks.uiuc.edu/Research/quantum_biology/</ref>。量子生物学以量子力学效应为根据，借助[[数学|数学]]计算，对生物学相互作用进行模拟<ref>http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2007/01/070116133617.htm Science Daily ''Quantum Biology: Powerful Computer Models Reveal Key Biological Mechanism'' Retrieved Oct 14, 2007</ref>。[[奧地利人|奧地利]]出生的[[量子物理学|量子物理学家]]和[[數理生物學|数理生物学家]][[埃尔温·薛定谔|埃尔温·薛定谔]]早在1946年就提出了用量子理论研究[[遗传系统|遗传系统]]的需求，[[理论生物学家|理论生物学家]][[罗伯特·罗森|罗伯特·罗森]]在1961年接着给出了一份详细、正式的研究量子遗传学的办法。在这方面的一个仍未解决的存在争议的问题是：[[量子效应|量子效应]]在[[生物系统|生物系统]]中的非平凡/通用角色（即不受限于[[分子|分子]]性质）究竟是什么？<ref>H.M. Wiseman, J. Eisert Nontrivial quantum effects in biology: A skeptical physicists' view arXiv:0705.1232v2 [physics.gen-ph]</ref><ref>Davies PC.Does quantum mechanics play a non-trivial role in life? Biosystems. 2004 Dec;78(1-3):69-79.</ref><ref>Ogryzko VV. Erwin Schrödinger, Francis Crick and epigenetic stability.Biol Direct. 2008 Apr 17;3:15.[http://www.biology-direct.com/content/3/1/15] [http://arxiv.org/abs/0906.4279] </ref>然而，新近关于[[转录|转录]]的研究与[[转录酶|转录酶]]对于[[相干态双链DNA|相干态双链DNA]]的[[量子信息处理|量子信息处理]]是一致的<ref>Cooper WG.Evidence for transcriptase quantum processing implies entanglement and decoherence of superposition proton states. BioSystems. 2009 Aug; 97:73-89.doi:10.1016/j.biosystems.2009.04.010</ref><ref>Cooper WG. Necessity of quantum coherence to account for the spectrum of time-dependent mutations exhibited by bacteriophage T4. Biochem. Genet. 2009 Oct; doi:10.1007/s10528-009-9293-8</ref>。

== 研究内容 ==
相关量子过程被研究的生物学现象主要包括对辐射的频率特异性吸收（出现在光合作用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lbl.gov/Science-Articles/Archive/PBD-quantum-secrets.html |title=Quantum Secrets of Photosynthesis Revealed |accessdate=2010-07-19 |archive-date=2017-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022070313/http://www2.lbl.gov/Science-Articles/Archive/PBD-quantum-secrets.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[视觉系统|视觉系统]]等内）<ref>{{cite book | last = Garab| first = G.| title = Photosynthesis: Mechanisms and Effects: Proceedings of the XIth International Congress on Photosynthesis| publisher = Kluwer Academic Publishers| date = 1999| isbn = 978-0792355472}}</ref>、[[化学能|化学能]]到[[机械能|机械能]]的转化<ref>{{cite book | last = Levine| first = Raphael D. | title = Molecular Reaction Dynamics| url = https://archive.org/details/molecularreactio00levi_0| publisher = Cambridge University Press| date = 2005| pages = [https://archive.org/details/molecularreactio00levi_0/page/16 16]–18| isbn = 978-0521842761}}</ref>、[[动物|动物]]的[[磁感應|磁感應]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Binhi| first = Vladimir N.| title = Magnetobiology: Underlying Physical Problems| url = https://archive.org/details/magnetobiologyun00binh_968| publisher = Academic Press| date = 2002| pages = [https://archive.org/details/magnetobiologyun00binh_968/page/n24 14]–16| isbn = 978-0121000714}}</ref>及许多[[细胞过程|细胞过程]]中的[[布朗马达|布朗马达]]<ref>{{cite book | last = Harald Krug| first = Harald Brune, Gunter Schmid, Ulrich Simon, Viola Vogel, Daniel Wyrwa, Holger Ernst, Armin Grunwald, Werner Grunwald, Heinrich Hofmann | title = Nanotechnology: Assessment and Perspectives| url = https://archive.org/details/nanotechnologyas00brun_489| publisher = Springer-Verlag Berlin and Heidelberg GmbH & Co. K| date = 2006| pages = [https://archive.org/details/nanotechnologyas00brun_489/page/n208 197]–240| isbn = 978-3540328193}}</ref>。该领域还在积极地研究[[磁场|磁场]]及[[鸟类|鸟类]]导航的量子分析<ref>http://rodgers.org.uk/research/ Chris Rodgers, ''The Spin Chemistry of Bird Navigation'' 2005</ref>并可能为许多[[生物体|生物体]]的[[昼夜节律|昼夜节律]]（[[生理节律|生理节律]]）的研究提供线索<ref>http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2007/08/070827174303.htm ''Math Model For Circadian Rhythm Created,'' ScienceDaily, August 30, 2007</ref>。

最近的研究已经确定了在[[光合作用|光合作用]]的光收获阶段，不同的色素的激发态之间的[[量子相干性|量子相干性]]和[[量子纠缠|纠缠]]。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Sarovar|first=Mohan|coauthors=Ishizaki, Akihito; Fleming, Graham R.; Whaley, K. Birgitta|title=Quantum entanglement in photosynthetic light-harvesting complexes|journal=Nature Physics|year=2010|volume=6|issue=6|pages=462–467|doi=10.1038/nphys1652|bibcode = 2010NatPh...6..462S |arxiv = 0905.3787 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal| author=Engel GS, Calhoun TR, Read EL, Ahn TK, Mancal T, Cheng YC et al.| title=Evidence for wavelike energy transfer through quantum coherence in photosynthetic systems. | journal=Nature | year= 2007 | volume= 446 | issue= 7137 | pages= 782–6 | pmid=17429397 | doi=10.1038/nature05678 | url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v446/n7137/abs/nature05678.html |bibcode = 2007Natur.446..782E }}</ref>尽管这一阶段的光合作用效率非常高，但是目前仍不清楚这些量子效应究竟如何，或者是否是生物学上相关的。<ref>{{cite journal| author=Scholes GS | title=Quantum-Coherent Electronic Energy Transfer: Did Nature Think of It First? | journal=Journal of Physical Chemistry Letters | year= 2010 | volume= 1 | pages= 2–8 | doi=10.1021/jz900062f }}</ref>

